              Classpert Index Tool
            </h2>
            <ul class='el:m-list el:amx-Fs(0.875em)'>
              <li class='el:amx-Mb(1em)'>
                <%= link_to get_listed_path, class: 'el:amx-C_fgV c-link c-link--white' do %>
                  <%= image_pack_tag('media/svg/flask.svg', class: 'el:amx-Mr(0.125em)', style: "vertical-align:bottom;width:1.125em;height:1.125em") %> Get Listed <sup>beta</sup>
